## services/geminiService.ts

-   Refactored mock data logic into reusable helper functions (`getMockSocialContent`, `getMockImage`).
-   Updated `generateSocialContent`, `generateImage`, `generateCampaignPlan`, and `analyzeIncomingMessage` to catch `429` (and other) errors.
